 android:pathData="M19,4h-1V2h-2v2H8V2H6v2H5C3.89,4 3.01,4.9 3.01,6L3,20c0,1.1 0.89,2 2,2h14c1.1,0 2,-0.9 2,-2V6C21,4.9 20.1,4 19,4zM19,20H5V10h14V20zM9,14H7v-2h2V14zM13,14h-2v-2h2V14zM17,14h-2v-2h2V14zM9,18H7v-2h2V18zM13,18h-2v-2h2V18zM17,18h-2v-2h2V18z"/>
</vector>
```

This implementation creates a nice bottom navigation bar with Home and Calendar tabs. You can easily add more tabs by adding more items to the `navItems` list. The navigation handles preserving state when switching between tabs and ensures efficient navigation without creating unnecessary back stack entries."},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<user_query>
