 // Your form UI implementation
 // ...
}
```

This implementation:
1. Adds a "Create Reminder" button to your calendar screen
2. Passes the selected date and bookable date as URL parameters when navigating
3. Sets up a route that accepts these date parameters
4. Creates an AddReminderScreen that uses the preselected dates

When users click the "Create Reminder" button, they'll be taken to the reminder creation form with the date already filled in."}]}
